A Python 3.8+ implementation of the Language Server Protocol.

Fork of the python-language-server project, maintained by the Spyder IDE
team and the community.

LSP Server Features:
- Auto Completion
- Autoimport
- Code Linting
- Code actions
- Signature Help
- Go to definition
- Hover
- Find References
- Document Symbols
- Document Formatting
- Code folding
- Multiple workspaces
